"{\"uid\": \"thesouthafrican.com-sport-paris-olympics-2024-paris-olympics-2024-medal-production-on-track-despite-protests-national-mint\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Copyright Blue Sky Publications (Pty) Ltd. All Rights Reserved.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 63, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 15, \"end\": 18, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_UK\", \"score\": 0.9604245282062909, \"rank\": 0.038886574838403416, \"text\": \"Sky\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_UK\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_UK\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"thesouthafrican.com is a division of Blue Sky Publications Ltd. Reproduction without permission prohibited  Home\\u00bbSport\\u00bbParis Olympics 2024\\u00bbParis Olympics 2024 medal production on track despite protests  Production of the medals for the Paris Olympics 2024 remains on track despite protests and stoppages by staff since last month.\", \"from\": 65, \"to\": 395, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 107, \"end\": 110, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_UK\", \"score\": 0.9604245282062909, \"rank\": 0.038886574838403416, \"text\": \"Sky\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_UK\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_UK\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The French national mint said on Monday that production of the medals for theParis Olympics 2024remained on track despite protests and stoppages by staff since last month.\", \"from\": 397, \"to\": 568, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 401, \"end\": 407, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.6786020442888306, \"rank\": 0.4516788197174968, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Around 50 employees demonstrated in front of the mint's central Paris headquarters on Monday, claiming that stoppages over the last fortnight had \\\"blocked production\\\" of the medals ahead of the start of the Games on July 26.\", \"from\": 570, \"to\": 794, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 634, \"end\": 639, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999972715, \"rank\": 2.795528908960819e-12, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Production of the medals is not blocked,\\\" the mint said in a statement.\", \"from\": 796, \"to\": 868, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"All of the medals have been minted and we are at the finishing stage.\", \"from\": 870, \"to\": 940, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We will deliver on schedule and on time.\\\"\", \"from\": 941, \"to\": 982, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Protesting staff, represented by trade unions, want an \\\"Olympics bonus\\\" which is being paid to other state employees such as police officers and nurses who will have to work over theOlympics and Paralympics in July and August.\", \"from\": 984, \"to\": 1210, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Management of the mint have refused bonuses and are negotiating annual pay rises for their 430 staff, who are responsible for producing the roughly 5 000 gold, silver and bronze medals to be used during theGames.\", \"from\": 1212, \"to\": 1424, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The Paris Olympics 2024 medals are made from recycled metal and will each contain a small hexagon-shaped medallion cut from discarded metal from the original Eiffel Tower.\", \"from\": 1426, \"to\": 1597, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The design is by luxury French jeweller Chaumet.\", \"from\": 1599, \"to\": 1647, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1623, \"end\": 1629, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.6786020442888306, \"rank\": 0.4516788197174968, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The mint previously denied a report\\u00a0in January that it was struggling to find a suitable non-toxic substance to coat each medal.\", \"from\": 1649, \"to\": 1777, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The puddle iron used in the Eiffel Tower needs protection from air and humidity to prevent it from rusting.\", \"from\": 1779, \"to\": 1886, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"By Garrin Lambley \\u00a9 Agence France-Presse    WIN R2 000: Take The South African's SASSA Survey  The South African is hiring!\", \"from\": 1888, \"to\": 2011, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1898, \"end\": 1905, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lambley_railway_station\", \"score\": 0.9377063948081237, \"rank\": 0.06643186553293795, \"text\": \"Lambley\", \"types\": [\"Q719456\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lambley_railway_station\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lambley_railway_station\"}, {\"begin\": 1908, \"end\": 1928, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Agence_France-Presse\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Agence France-Presse\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Agence_France-Presse\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Agence_France-Presse\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Freelance writing positions available  Follow The South African on Facebook for the latest local and international news  Follow The South African's WhatsApp channel for the latest sport, lifestyle and local news  Follow The South African on X for the latest, breaking news  A brand new shopping mall is coming to Pretoria East, bringing major retailers and new convenience to the area.\", \"from\": 2012, \"to\": 2397, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2160, \"end\": 2168, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/WhatsApp\", \"score\": 0.9997187840905598, \"ran